{"tid":1896562,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE 將進軍美國！與當地有力唱片公司簽訂夥伴合約","createTime":"2020-02-25T08:04:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T17:17:41.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0bb10ca848bd88d29dfe9e95b21632054a472b8e","tid":1896562,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T08:04:53.000Z","msg":"出道約四年半、在亞洲享有獨特地位的 TWICE，如今也要準備進軍美國市場了！<br />\n<br />\nJYP Entertainment 為尋求資源支援 TWICE 在美國的活動，最近和環球音樂集團 (UMG) 旗下的 Republic Records 簽訂了夥伴合約。該品牌是美國最有力的品牌之一，包括 Ariana Grande、Taylor Swift⋯⋯等知名歌手都隸屬旗下。<br />\n<br />\n隨著這項消息底定，Republic Records 也透露 TWICE 即將阿行新歌，令人期待她們接下來即將展開的全新發展。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，因為 COVID-19 疫情持續在韓國擴散，TWICE 原定於 3 月 7、8 兩日為世界巡迴演唱會《TWICELIGHTS》在首爾舉行的壓軸場演出已確定取消。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/124559\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Fnews%2F124559&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpSrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=f90af018\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/124559</a>"},{"pid":"9b5b121dbd96ce560fab09b50e31451f8cb2ea95","tid":1896562,"uid":192307,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T08:12:05.000Z","msg":"Twice 勁到"},{"pid":"24150a2362dc192f9d0e92642156ea937b2a8692","tid":1896562,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9b5b121dbd96ce560fab09b50e31451f8cb2ea95","tid":1896562,"uid":192307,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T08:12:05.000Z","msg":"Twice 勁到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T08:13:24.000Z","msg":"I am the once ar diu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2e11a22f832550621e55016ba4c9870b2df47c","tid":1896562,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T08:14:16.000Z","msg":"美國夢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa